From 78d1dfb0c53cc3303bdf51c11cb79ab417905a65 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Huy Dev <innercoach.net@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 22 May 2026 09:27:01 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix(notifications): tighten Web Push delivery scope

Keep push subscriptions bound to their original principal, restrict org-level pushes to active users, and avoid sensitive system notification previews outside the app.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
